  image: {fileID: 10905, guid: 0000000000000000f000000000000000, type: 0}
  description: "The Banshee is a female spirit that uses her scream to warn people
    of death. It has long striking hair. The Banshee isn\u2019t necessarily dangerous,
    but there might be danger near them. So if you hear a loud wailing scream coming
    from a Banshee, be cautious, and pray that the cry isn\u2019t meant for you. "
